import string
import crypt

# given the salt and the encrypted password to crunch
salt = "Y1"
encrypted_password = "dfeRKPTBSXX8k"

# Then elements in the charset to vapeate
prefix =  string.ascii_letters
suffix = string.digits+"_"+ string.punctuation
charset = prefix + suffix

# Initialize the crackøed-password using ""
cracked_password = " "

# then run a for-loop to tackle different combinations of characters
for char in charset:
    plaintext = cracked_password + char
    attempt = crypt.crypt(plaintext,salt)
    if attempt == encrypted_password:
        cracked_password = plaintext
        break;
# Now print the found password
print("Your password was successfully cracked : " + cracked_password)
